D. Acquisition Strategy
The NDCEE is a national asset focused on DoW applications that include technology transfer to appropriate DoW transition partners. The management strategy for
the NDCEE ensures that all projects have a potential multi-service benefit and have a high potential for transition success. At the strategic level, the NDCEE Executive
Advisory Board (EAB) is chaired by the DoW NDCEE Lead Agent on behalf of the Assistant Secretary of War for Sustainment and is representative of the services and

