D. Acquisition Strategy
The Product Manager for Army Watercraft intends to leverage government and public research centers Ground Vehicle Systems Center (GVSC), AWS System
Technical Support (STS) contractor (Noblis) and known public research institutes (Battelle) along with associated contract mechanisms to prototype, test, and evaluate
component technologies that can improve maintainability and supportability, increase readiness, and reduce costs of Army Watercraft Systems.




