against near-peer threats. This effort will mature wide-band, multi-function RF, aperture technology developed under Army
Science and Technology (S&T) to deliver an advanced payload that significantly increases range, accuracy and survivability of
current airborne surveillance radar systems to the High Accuracy Detection and Exploitation System (HADES) program. This effort


