A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This Engineering and Manufacturing Development (EMD) PE manages the Soldier as a system, with the goal of increasing Soldiers' combat effectiveness, increasing
survivability, and improving the Soldiers' quality of life. It develops and tests prototypes of weapons, clothing, equipment, and other items useful to support the Soldier.

PE 0604601A: Infantry Support Weapons                                        UNCLASSIFIED
