of-systems capabilities for evaluation and integration, using current Systems Engineering and Technical Assistance (SETA) contracts, Federally Funded Research and
Development Center personnel (FFRDCs) as necessary, plus tools/deliverables built under project CF2. The ASA/SIF will develop a metric-based approach that will
include virtual, constructive and live evaluations and tools across the Department of War (DoW), academia and industry which will be used for senior leaders to make


