D. Acquisition Strategy
The Army will coordinate plans with USW (R&E), DTRA, and other Services to prototype and demonstrate CIED technologies, with Army and Service Laboratories
and/or industry performing the demonstration activities. The Army will use existing and new contracts to perform these efforts with selected industry partners based
on solicitations issued. The Army will continue promising technology demonstrations started in FY 2020 by DTRA based on review with DTRA, USW (R&E) and other
Services.




